<span class="dim">Weekly editions · 2,500-3,500 words · Research-grade</span></pre>

    <pre class="term-block al" data-d="400"><span class="phosphor">WHAT YOU GET</span>

<span class="amber">The Signal</span> — single most important development this week
<span class="amber">The Map</span> — where major players moved and why
<span class="amber">The Edge</span> — analysis nobody else is talking about
