Every prediction falsifiable with specific dates.
Every miss published alongside every hit.</pre>

    <pre class="term-block al" data-d="600"><span class="phosphor">WHY THIS EXISTS</span>

Everyone is drowning in AI content.
Nobody knows what actually matters.

The Brief exists because ZERO already built the engine
