    <div class="product-cta-block al" data-d="1000">
      <div class="cta-price-row">
        <span class="cta-price">$29<span class="cta-period">/mo</span></span>
        <span class="cta-label">LAUNCH PRICE</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-subtext">Weekly intelligence · Cancel anytime · Price rises after early editions</div>
      <a href="https://newsletter.getzero.dev/upgrade" class="cta-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SUBSCRIBE →</a>
      <div class="cta-proof">
        <span class="phosphor">1</span> paying subscriber · <span class="phosphor">Edition #1</span> shipped · <span class="phosphor">4</span> predictions on record
      </div>
    </div>

    <pre class="term-block al" data-d="1200"><span class="phosphor">THE ENGINE</span>

This isn't an analyst with a newsletter template.
The Brief is produced by an intelligence system:

<span class="amber">→</span> <span class="phosphor">70</span> entities tracked across repos, accounts, narratives
